## Development

Install dependencies and run the server with the native Python toolchain:

```sh
uv sync --extra dev
{{#if (eq pythonWebFramework "fastapi")}}
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port ${PORT:-8000}
{{else if (eq pythonWebFramework "litestar")}}
uv run litestar --app src.app.main:app run --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port ${PORT:-8000}
{{else}}
uv run python -m app.main
{{/if}}
```

The health endpoint is available at `/health`.
